{"tid":158661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［生活物理學］係男人識痾尿既就入黎研究下","createTime":"2017-03-16T12:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T16:31:36.000Z","uid":91326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f26092c9e0d1d828474999ade543c4f796e52f1","tid":158661,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"各位威猛既男士，大家有冇發覺次次對著尿兜痾既時候，硬係會有小小水花反彈落條褲或者鞋道，舊鞋舊褲都由佢，有時著新鞋真係痛都心埋，皮鞋更加彈到有水積好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘗試解決方法<br />\n1:去廁格，但唔係成日有，同fd去又比人以為自己係幼龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2:企開小小，但企太開有時個個望著哂，去到埋尾閘水又滴到人地成地都係，唔係完美解決方法<br />\n<br />\n3:重點既入射角與反射角，打斜向兩邊位入佢，可以減低最多回彈既機會，但現實生活中始終都係有幾滴因為水力大而反彈<br />\n<br />\n研究下有冇解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb112e89bf08d311a4f3fe6133e0477775703e2","tid":158661,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"倒立"},{"pid":"dbe1e3f1ad9f4582fabd3534e77907780bdaaa93","tid":158661,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倒立</blockquote><br />\n咁重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9534bda19d63b58acb5983bdafb9150ae1ebe3a","tid":158661,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"倒立"},{"pid":"8e293116dc8962592bd57f673ac707919c1d8460","tid":158661,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"連登咁多絲打嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c95a7ba2e7de074c87c3a6d537de4a1f6d4